1) Install SSh Agent plugin
   Configure via pipeline syntax with Apply username of that server and private key from copy putty.

2) Add maven path in Jenkins.

3) Add worker node. ad click on launch agent.
so it will create workspace on node (In the path of your remote working dir. on the host)
Shh Agent is used to scp only.

4) Add Dockerhub credentials in jenkins and referenve in jenkinsfile environmnets section

5) Create webhooks in github and add its code into checkout stage.



